<P>
"We strongly support China's entry into the World Trade
Organization and hope to have closer cooperation with China in the
future." Jacobs said.
</P>
<P>
He also disclosed that APL has ordered over 34,000 containers
from a Chinese container manufacturer.
</P>
<P>
APL, owned by Singapore's Neptune Orient Lines (NOL), has 30
branches in China. 
</P>
