growth in August, with monthly output value increasing 12.8
percent year on year to 201.2 billion yuan (24 billion U.S.
dollars).
</P>
<P>
According to figures released by the National Bureau of
Statistics Monday, total industrial output value for the January-
August period amounted to 1,496.8 billion yuan (180 billion U.S.
dollars), 11.6 percent more than in the same period last year.
</P>
