<HEADLINE> WEF Summit Held in Melbourne, Australia </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
As the meeting cite has been surrounded by thousands of
protesters against the globlization of economy, the opening
ceremony was forced to delay for nearly 20 minutes. By midday,
nearly half of the meeting participants failed to enter the
complex.
</P>
<P>
A delegate attending the meeting told Xinhua that he would be
sent to the Casino complex by boat as all the land gates were
blocked by protesters.
</P>
<P>
"The present situation is that no body outside can enter into
and no body inside can get out," he said.
</P>
<P>
The Crown Cosino is located on the bank of the Yarra River.
