first in this week, followed by other regions in the next few days,
it said.
</P>
<P>
Thai fishermen should be more careful and follow weather
conditions closely, as wind and waves in the Andaman Sea have been
strong, said the statement.
</P>
<P>
The northeast provinces are still struggling to recover from
the Kaemi tropical storm, which caused some 605 million baht (14.7
million U.S. dollars) of damages weeks ago. 
