<HEADLINE> China Has 12 Million Teachers </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
BEIJING, September 11 (Xinhua) -- China's population of
teachers totaled 12 million by the end of last year, which means
that there is a teacher for every 20 students in China.
</P>
<P>
According to statistics from the Ministry of Education, there
are 14.88 million teaching and administrative staff, including 11.
79 million teachers, for 244 million students.
</P>
<P>
The teachers work at 860,000 schools ranging from kindergartens
to colleges. 
</P>
